Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:02.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:07.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:14.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:35.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:45.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:56.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:02.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:08.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:23.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:02.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:07.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:14.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:35.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:45.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:56.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:02.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:06.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:23.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两台敌机接近本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开炮 攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人的话 就和你们没有分别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的话又会伤害无辜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你们的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲太前了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不了手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手下留情? 还是想侮辱我?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 超度你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 就等你出这杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然如此棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再放手了 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超负荷?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…机体不是万全的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有打倒的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 包围双炉机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Drive…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam全机后退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·诺列嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打断敌人的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鱼雷释放高浓度粒子和烟幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 有烟幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可视通信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交战空域出现烟幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子量增大 和MS队通信中断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里才改变战术?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整态势 下达撤退指令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios机体无法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios没反应?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用任务记录器确定Arios的交战地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容00后 Seravee和Cherudim开始搜索Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你实在太独断专行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯中尉的AHEAD失踪?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即编成搜查班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么向史米卢佐夫上校交代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退A-LAWS了吗 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会输给你这个次品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽·帕珐西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒…路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 你想起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒…路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽·帕珐西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 不必劳您亲自出马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照记录器的记录应该是这空域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脑量子波感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击中尉的 也都是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返舰命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止对中尉的搜索?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上层的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们部队专心攻击天人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的搜查就交给正规军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim已出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee到达弹射甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚 Arios的交战空域已传给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量避免与A-LAWS交战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·艾迪 出动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee已出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即进入潜航准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 不是告诉你不能用TRANS-AM吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好在Twin Drive还在运作状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理就拜托您了 阿勒路亚他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗 让你修理Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在KATARON的人平安逃离之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去检查了机体 都是系统DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法修理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援不知何时会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你变成了索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是植入了其他人格 复原了失去的五感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人机关把我作为超兵送进军队 想借此维持组织的存续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因此才能见到你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就认出是你 可能是脑量子波的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到能和你这样对话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我好吗 你逃离超人机关后的故事  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免被废弃 和同伴一起逃离设施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初后悔应该带你走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 幸亏没那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同伴夺取运输船逃出卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根本无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续漂流 舰内的食物和氧气终将耗尽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不想死 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你体内有另一个人格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法否认 哈雷路亚就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一幸存的我诅咒命运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒超人机关和这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以甘愿成为Gundam Meister改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵能做的只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 索玛·比利斯的记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在 包括她的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该明白我做过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了同胞 用这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两次夺走了大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又何尝不是…夺走过你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的攻击下 我杀死了另一个你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 这是索玛·比利斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样 比利斯就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对不起 我不知该如何补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 知道索玛·比利斯是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直想着你 想救出你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在实现了 我又不知该为你做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我 根本没有什么能为你做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在身边就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 终于和你相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有五感 只能用脑量子波呼唤的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你给了我回应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有你 我才感激自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用这双眼睛看着你 能和你说话 能触摸你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会有这样的时刻到来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机体?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗 全员集中到中央区域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻男子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你就是当时的Gundam机师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开中尉身边 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路辛苦了 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 第三支部被敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在为重逢高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 联邦政府终于对中东动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦受袭后正规军进入 听说建立了临时政府
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时政府…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 阿撒迪斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦以临时政府为中心将各国解体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说要重建中东
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解体 重建中东
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 阿撒迪斯坦王国已不复存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…阿撒迪斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人格被覆盖?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 现在的我不是索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛丽 玛丽·帕珐西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 这是中尉的真名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人机关连这种事都做得出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽是个温柔的女孩 不会伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把玛丽交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到联邦和A-LAWS的话 她又会被作为超兵利用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是天人成员 和你在一起中尉也会被卷入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没蠢到相信恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为你的…不 你们愚蠢的行径 失去了众多同胞和部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这仇我还没忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 玛丽…\N不 请发誓再也不让索玛·比利斯卷入战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 玛丽 只要你能幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才索玛·比利斯中尉光荣战死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须返回报告给上级  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 还没道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前低轨道站的事故 感谢协助救援行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史米卢佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您只让索玛·比利斯参加对Gundam的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这语气 看来真的不是我认识的中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我身体里的索玛·比利斯说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想成为您的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 有这一句话就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他幸福地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢一直以来的照顾 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报到 在下是\N超人机关技术研究所派来的超兵一号 索玛·比利斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁人·桃子 我的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Gundam的王牌吗 但她还是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉是第一次品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去战斗 少尉
