Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有高兴事谁都会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
