Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有失去战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 似乎和女朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.27,0:23:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
